770
00:31:28,412 --> 00:31:29,780
- A sense of urgency.
- A sense of urgency.

771
00:31:30,114 --> 00:31:32,883
We can say it went to Da-hee's room.

772
00:31:32,950 --> 00:31:34,852
- After passing Do-yeon's room?
- Good.

773
00:31:35,152 --> 00:31:36,887
<i>- We'll send this one first.</i>
<i>- Okay.</i>

774
00:31:36,954 --> 00:31:38,689
<i>- It sounds good.</i>
<i>- I also like the idea.</i>

775
00:31:39,256 --> 00:31:40,424
<i>What can we say next?</i>

776
00:31:41,158 --> 00:31:42,426
- Send that photo first.
- Yes.

777
00:31:42,493 --> 00:31:44,461
We can make more
after checking how they react.

778
00:31:44,528 --> 00:31:46,697
I'll share this on our group chat.

779
00:31:46,764 --> 00:31:49,032
Say, "Shut the front door.
A pigeon flew into the house."

780
00:31:49,099 --> 00:31:50,134
"SHUT THE FRONT DOOR"?
SO OLD-FASHIONED

781
00:31:50,200 --> 00:31:51,935
PROUD OF HIMSELF

782
00:31:52,169 --> 00:31:53,570
I'm having a blast.

783
00:31:54,571 --> 00:31:56,073
