795
00:32:17,995 --> 00:32:19,430
DEAD SERIOUS

796
00:32:19,496 --> 00:32:21,031
AHN JAE-HYEON
UNREAL! A PIGEON FLEW IN!

797
00:32:21,098 --> 00:32:22,933
