803
00:32:32,776 --> 00:32:34,511
LIPS GOING DRY FROM NERVES

804
00:32:34,578 --> 00:32:36,580
- It can be a good sign.
- Hey, look.

805
00:32:36,647 --> 00:32:37,648
My gosh.

806
00:32:37,981 --> 00:32:40,050
THEY RECEIVE THE SECOND PHOTO

807
00:32:40,117 --> 00:32:41,852
- What's this?
- Hey, it's your room!

808
00:32:41,919 --> 00:32:44,621
AHN JAE-HYEON
IT'S GONE INTO YOUR GUYS' ROOMS

809
00:32:44,688 --> 00:32:46,490
It must've gone to your room
from my room.

810
00:32:46,557 --> 00:32:47,791
CHANGES HER ATTITUDE RIGHT AWAY

811
00:32:47,858 --> 00:32:48,859
SIGHS

812
00:32:50,527 --> 00:32:54,398
IMAGINE DA-HEE'S SPOTLESS ROOM

813
00:32:54,798 --> 00:32:58,635
FILLED WITH A FLOCK OF PIGEONS

814
00:32:58,702 --> 00:33:00,704
THE FOOTAGE HAS AI-GENERATED CONTENT

815
00:33:00,771 --> 00:33:03,440
STRESS LEVEL SPIKING

816
00:33:03,507 --> 00:33:04,508
What on earth?

817
00:33:04,975 --> 00:33:06,376
What's going on?

818
00:33:06,443 --> 00:33:07,911
TRYING HER BEST NOT TO LOSE HER COOL

819
