820
00:33:10,047 --> 00:33:11,715
- I said we should.
- A call will seal the deal.

821
00:33:11,782 --> 00:33:12,816
Yes, exactly.

822
00:33:13,050 --> 00:33:15,419
- Let's do rock-paper-scissors first.
- Rock-paper-scissors?

823
00:33:15,486 --> 00:33:16,954
- Okay.
- All of us are doing it?

824
00:33:17,020 --> 00:33:18,021
You snooze, you lose.

825
00:33:18,088 --> 00:33:20,190
- Rock, paper, scissors!
- Rock, paper, scissors!

826
00:33:20,257 --> 00:33:23,494
THE BURDEN FALLS ON JAE-HYEON
WHO'S THE WORST LIAR AMONG THEM

827
00:33:24,294 --> 00:33:28,131
AS LONG AS IT'S NOT ME

828
00:33:28,198 --> 00:33:30,367
Give us your method acting!

829
00:33:30,434 --> 00:33:32,970
Show us how it's done, Jae-hyeon!

830
00:33:33,036 --> 00:33:35,672
They might actually believe it
