831
00:33:35,739 --> 00:33:37,407
- Exactly.
- You're the calmest of us all.

832
00:33:37,474 --> 00:33:39,042
- I'm the last person they'd believe.
- Right.

833
00:33:39,109 --> 00:33:40,477
- Same here.
- You have to do it.

834
00:33:40,777 --> 00:33:42,246
Tell them we're after the pigeons.

835
00:33:42,312 --> 00:33:44,147
But the four of us failed to catch it

836
00:33:44,214 --> 00:33:46,350
and the staff has gotten involved.

837
00:33:46,416 --> 00:33:47,718
