853
00:34:18,148 --> 00:34:20,551
WITNESS THE PASSIONATE PERFORMANCE
OF VETERAN ACTORS

854
00:34:20,617 --> 00:34:22,986
WHO HAVE 76 YEARS
OF EXPERIENCE IN TOTAL

855
00:34:23,654 --> 00:34:24,922
