- The date isn't guaranteed.

1574
00:59:15,177 --> 00:59:16,812
Freaking really?

1575
00:59:16,879 --> 00:59:18,647
THAT IS...

1576
00:59:19,014 --> 00:59:20,282
Freaking really?

1577
